These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
City: hannover, nizza, berlin, miami
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, june, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
4. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
5. the person traveling to miami is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
7. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's birthday is in february##7
8. the person traveling to nizza and the person who's birthday is in august have the same parity positions##9
9. the person traveling to berlin and the person who's birthday is in october have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | hannover | nizza | berlin     | miami |
| Pet           | june   | august     | february | october  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
City: edinburgh, hannover, miami, london
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, german
1. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
2. the german and the person traveling to hannover have the same parity positions##9
3. the indonesian is not to the right of the italian##8
4. the dutch is not to the right of the person traveling to london##8
5. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
7. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
8. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | london     | miami    | edinburgh | hannover    |
| Hobby      | dutch | indonesian | italian      | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, gospel, rock, techno
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
2. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the fan rock##5
3. the fan gospel is on the left of the fan rock##1
4. the fan gospel is on the far left##1
5. the fan r&b is on the right of the fan rock##1
6. the fan rock is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person playing canasta##8
8. the fan gospel and the person playing canasta have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | gospel    | rock   | r&b    | techno  |
| Food       | canasta | mah-jongg | monopoly | snooker |

