.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, july, february, august
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bongani, pall-mall, baccarat
1. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august and the baccarat-smoker have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | august | february | october  | july |
| Music-Genre   | pall-mall             | bongani          | baccarat | montecristo    |

