.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, white, chestnut, yellow
House: tower, art-deco, modern, cape-cod
1. the person who likes chestnut is not the modern house##6
2. the tower house and the person who likes blue have different parity positions##9
3. the art-deco house and the person who likes white have different parity positions##9
4. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
5. the tower house is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
6. the person who likes white is not the art-deco house##6
7. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
8. the tower house is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
9. the cape-cod house is not the person who likes yellow##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | blue | chestnut | yellow  | white |
| Pet           | art-deco   | tower     | modern | cape-cod      |

