.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, card-games, video-games, filmmaking
There 4 different types of food: corn, radish, lemon, kale
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
4. the person eating corn and the person who's hobby is video-games have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person eating corn have different parity positions##9
6. the person eating lemon is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
7. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person eating kale##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | card-games | rock-climbing | video-games | filmmaking |
| Nationality   | kale        | lemon    | corn   | radish |

