.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting, biathlon, climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, bus, jet-ski, boat
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
2. the person driving the bus and the person who's sport is biathlon have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person driving the boat##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | weightlifting | ice-hockey | biathlon | climbing |
| Pet   | jet-ski         | boat | bus    | tram   |

