.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-8::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, chinchilla, mouse
4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, scrabble, chess
1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
2. the person playing chess is between the person playing bridge and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person playing chess and the owner of the mouse have different parity positions##9
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | hamster    | lizard | mouse         | chinchilla     |
| Sport         | bridge | chess  | scrabble | backgammon |

