2. the gothic-revival house is not to the right of the ranch-style house##8
3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the designer is on the left of the chef##1
5. the chef is not the townhouse house##6
6. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
7. the designer and the ranch-style house have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | designer | chef | freelancer | dressmaker |
| Pet     | gothic-revival     | modern     | ranch-style     | townhouse    |

