The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, sailing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person playing go##8
2. the person playing whist and the person who's sport is skateboarding have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
5. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is skateboarding##7
6. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | scrabble | go   | mah-jongg | whist |
| Transport   | sailing   | biathlon | swimming    | skateboarding      |

