2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
3. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person driving the roller##8
4. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
8. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the person driving the roller and the person who's sport is skiing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | helicopter   | roller    | subway | car    |
| Nationality   | lacrosse | skiing | sailing   | skateboarding |

