.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, may, april
House: art-deco, palace, townhouse, cape-cod
 1. the person who's birthday is in june and the townhouse house have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 3. the art-deco house is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in september##7
 4. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 6. the townhouse house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in april and the palace house have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 9. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the art-deco house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | september  | april | may  | june |
| Music-Genre   | cape-cod | townhouse     | art-deco | palace     |

