2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the american is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
4. the italian is not to the right of the malaysian##8
5. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the ship and the egyptian have the same parity positions##9
7. the person driving the skateboard and the american have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | egyptian | italian | malaysian | american |
| Pet   | ship    | trike   | boat        | skateboard            |

