2. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person watching animation movies and the person playing chess have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fantasy    | animation | spy | romance |
