.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
4 different games are played: billiard, chess, monopoly, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy, western, scientific
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
 4. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching zombie movies is not the person playing chess##6
 6. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 7. the person playing scrabble and the person watching comedy movies have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8
 9. the person playing scrabble is the person watching comedy movies##1
10. the person playing chess and the person watching comedy movies have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | chess    | monopoly        | scrabble   | billiard      |
| Hobby      | scientific | western | comedy | zombie |

 